      "text": "Vibe Coding 核心实践",
      "fontSize": 22.598403058301216,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Vibe Coding 核心实践",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 401,
      "index": "b4x",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "UG-MMfSlkK5Yqbb0ePVLX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 389.79721054491773,
      "y": 3740.6723229430418,
      "width": 350.8762472961452,
      "height": 105.26931177303797,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "0cMmcUohTAbU82Ls9Bin1",
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1770720557553,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "versionNonce": 1201918636,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 570878100,
      "text": "• 先确保能跑起来，再谈理解和改造\n• MVP 验证是关键：证明价值后才值得深入\n• Spec 驱动设计：从二开视角重新规划 Phase\n• 工程收敛：保持代码整洁，移除非必要文件\n• 持续交付：版本管理 + 部署上线",
      "fontSize": 16.843089883686083,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• 先确保能跑起来，再谈理解和改造\n• MVP 验证是关键：证明价值后才值得深入\n• Spec 驱动设计：从二开视角重新规划 Phase\n• 工程收敛：保持代码整洁，移除非必要文件\n• 持续交付：版本管理 + 部署上线",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 403,
      "index": "b4y",
      "autoResize": true
    },
