      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1770720557553,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "versionNonce": 421010324,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 322257172,
      "text": "传统思维：理解 → 设计 → 开发 → 验证\n\nVibe 思维：运行 → 验证 → 理解 → 设计 → 改造\n\n核心：验证过才值得理解，能跑的代码优于完美的设计",
      "fontSize": 15.65101688341708,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "传统思维：理解 → 设计 → 开发 → 验证\n\nVibe 思维：运行 → 验证 → 理解 → 设计 → 改造\n\n核心：验证过才值得理解，能跑的代码优于完美的设计",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 383,
      "index": "b51",
      "autoResize": true
    },
